result.title: Round 2
result.content:
It's time for a new contest.

This is my first contest to write so I hope you like it.

Here is some tips you need to take care of:

-Read the statements well.

-If you have any problem during the contest you can ask us for help.

-Google is your friend.

-Try to have fun as much as you can.

I want to thank Mr.AAA and ahmdalgendi for testing the statements and test cases.
